com.ibm.maximo.oslc

Class Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.maximo.oslc.Options

  • public class Options
extends Object
    Options is served for MaximoConnector.

    The following code shows how to initial MaximoConnector using MaximoConnector and OptionsConstructor

     
 MaximoConnector mc = new MaximoConnector(new Options().user(userName)
 .password(password).mt(true).lean(false).auth(authMethod)
 .host(hostAddress).port(portNum));
